<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>LOOKA | Dressing Company</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      color: #222;
      background-color: #fff;
    }
    header {
      background: #000;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 20px 50px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }
    header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
    }
    nav a {
      color: #fff;
      margin-left: 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .hero {
      background: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1520974735194-6c65e4d94d5b') center/cover no-repeat;
      height: 80vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 50px;
      color: white;
    }
    .hero h2 {
      font-size: 48px;
      max-width: 500px;
    }
    section {
      padding: 60px 50px;
    }
    .about, .why {
      background: #f7f7f7;
    }
    .section-title {
      font-size: 32px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .collections {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
    }
    .card {
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    footer {
      background: #000;
      color: #fff;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <h1>LOOKA</h1>
  <nav>
    <a href="#">Home</a>
    <a href="#">About</a>
    <a href="#">Collections</a>
    <a href="#">Contact</a>
  </nav>
</header>

<div class="hero">
  <h2>Define Your Style with LOOKA</h2>
</div>

<section class="about">
  <h3 class="section-title">About LOOKA</h3>
  <p>
    LOOKA is a modern dressing company dedicated to creating stylish, comfortable,
    and confidence-boosting fashion for everyday life. Our designs blend simplicity
    with elegance to help you express your true look.
  </p>
</section>

<section>
  <h3 class="section-title">Our Collections</h3>
  <div class="collections">
    <div class="card">Men’s Wear</div>
    <div class="card">Women’s Wear</div>
    <div class="card">Casual Collection</div>
    <div class="card">Premium Dressing</div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="why">
  <h3 class="section-title">Why Choose LOOKA</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>✔ Premium quality fabrics</li>
    <li>✔ Modern & minimal designs</li>
    <li>✔ Affordable fashion</li>
    <li>✔ Trusted dressing brand</li>
  </ul>
</section>

<section>
  <h3 class="section-title">Contact Us</h3>
  <p>Email: info@looka.com</p>
  <p>Phone: +123 456 7890</p>
</section>

<footer>
  <p>©️ 2025 LOOKA Dressing Company. All Rights Reserved.</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>